main event: A military report of a UFO sighting at high altitude over the Pacific Ocean on 29 May 1963.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 3 minutes and involved one object,The object was initially sighted at a high elevation and moved during the observation,The object faded and reappeared twice while it was being observed,It reached a maximum brightness equivalent to a second magnitude star,Weather conditions were noted as clear with no unusual phenomena.
location: Pacific Ocean, Unknown Region, Unknown Country
